snippet.title: Sonic Project Scramble Trailer by Kafonn
snippet.description: This is a trailer for my platform fighting game. It features a lot of the mechanics and systems you can play with in the game and it also shows off some of Sonic and Knuckle's movesets, since they're the 2 finished characters so far. - Kafonn
